This folder contains a "built-in" version of the HepMC3 reference implementation
that includes only those components needed to build MARLEY. Source code for the
current version of the full HepMC3 library can be obtained from
https://gitlab.cern.ch/hepmc/HepMC3. The source code included in this folder is
redistributed under the terms of the GNU General Public License, version 3 or
later. All source files in this folder are copyright (C) 2014-2023 by the HepMC
Collaboration.
